OL,3,CEx-special constable jailed for life
OL,4,Cafter raping teen he groomed on
OL,5,CSnapchat
OL,7,FA former special constable who raped a
OL,8,F14-year-old shortly after being let
OL,9,Fout of prison for a 'strikingly
OL,10,Fsimilar offence' has been sent back to
OL,11,Fjail for life.
OL,13,FStephen Godridge arranged to pick up
OL,14,Fthe girl in his car and then took her
OL,15,Fto a park where he raped and sexually
OL,16,Fassaulted her.
