OL,4,Cafter raping teen he groomed on
OL,5,CSnapchat
OL,7,FThe 31-year-old had only been released
OL,8,Ffrom prison a few months prior, after
OL,9,Fexploiting two other young girls in
OL,10,Fcircumstances which were almost
OL,11,Fidentical.
OL,13,FPrior to his first conviction
OL,14,FGodridge, from Bolton, was a special
OL,15,Fconstable for Greater Manchester
OL,16,FPolice.
