OL,3,CEx-special constable jailed for life
OL,4,Cafter raping teen he groomed on
OL,5,CSnapchat
OL,7,FHe denied the new offences but
OL,8,Ffollowing a trial was found guilty of
OL,9,Ftwo counts of rape, sexual assaults,
OL,10,Fand breaching a sexual harm prevention
OL,11,Forder.
OL,13,FHe was sentenced to life with a
OL,14,Fminimum term of 10 years and eight
OL,15,Fmonths in prison.
OL,17,FIn a statement which was read out to
OL,18,Fthe court on her behalf, his victim
OL,19,Fsaid: "I'm scared that someone is
OL,20,Fgoing to come into my house and get
OL,21,Fme. I just can't stand being alone.
