OL,7,F"I feel so vulnerable that it's just
OL,8,Fgoing to happen again. I don't go out
OL,9,Fmuch any more.
OL,11,F"This incident repeats in my mind on a
OL,12,Fconstant replay. I'm scared he could
OL,13,Fhurt me or my family again."
OL,15,FPassing sentence, Judge Gary Woodhall
OL,16,Fsaid: "You were deliberately using
OL,17,FSnapchat as a platform to identify
OL,18,Fyoung girls for sexualised contact.
