OL,7,F"I am satisfied that you were looking
OL,8,Ffor girls you could meet with, isolate
OL,9,Fand then engage in sexual activity."
OL,11,FGodridge was also handed an indefinite
OL,12,Fsexual harm prevention order and told
OL,13,Fto sign the sex offenders' register
OL,14,Ffor life.
OL,16,FThe judge added: "Your previous
OL,17,Fsentence and protective order did
OL,18,Fnothing to prevent you from offending
OL,19,Fin an almost identical way again."
